Description: systemd: Use wrapper
 We use a wrapper script for various reasons.  See the script for details.
Forwarded: not-needed
Author: Richard Laager <rlaager@wiktel.com>
Last-Update: 2017-11-08
--- a/etc/ntpd.service
+++ b/etc/ntpd.service
